title: Morning Joe 4/12/22
description: Russian President Vladimir Putin is reported to be conducting a 'Stalinist' mass purge of Russian secret intelligence, dismissing about 150 Federal Security Bureau officers, including some who have been arrested, according to a Times of London report. The Morning Joe panel discusses.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
